**Qal** or **Hiph\`il** ?) ***Imperfect*** <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎ינין‎</span> [[BDB#Kt|Kt]]; &gt; **Niph\`al** <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎ינּוֺן‎</span> [[BDB#Qr|Qr]] [[Ps.72.17|Ps 72:17]] let his name ***have increase*** (or, if Niph\`al, ***be propagated, spread***); but dubious, [[BDB#Vrss|Vrss]] perhaps <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎יִכּוֺן‎</span> ***be established, endure***.
